                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/56998031/">林梁</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">引用了超多史料，比较喜欢里面讲张爱玲、胡适、杜月笙、高伯雨和张大千这几篇。浪花淘尽，风流人物，俱往矣。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
