                    <span id="c-919362811" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-919362811" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="919362811">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/asukafai/">夏言</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-05-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">我个人比较喜欢许寿裳之死和吴稚晖、章太炎为何别苗头的那两篇，虽然讲张爱玲和苏青的也不错然而我始终对男女感情什么的事儿不是特别感兴趣……（和单身狗没关系！）</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="978067416">
